                <div class="w3-container">
                    <p>A <b>leader </b>is simply a person who can <b>communicate, relate</b> and <b>lead</b> people to a <b>common mission </b>and actually put in <b>work.</b></p>
                    <p>My mentor made a very good point about this skillset; that I <b>"could teach anyone all the other invaluable skillsets but not this one!"</b></p>
                    <p>So, I don't have any tip here! It's within me! It's upto me!</p>
                    <p>But one thing I know is that, <b>to lead people</b>, one needs to have <b>content!</b></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
